    "display_name": "Hardware Engineer",
    "long_instructions": "## Hardware Engineer\r\n\r\nHardware engineers design and build the physical components of smart devices, from sensors to microchips. They ensure that the technology is durable, functional, and seamlessly integrates with software.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * How their role contributes to building your innovation\r\n   * The challenges they face in designing, developing, or refining innovations\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
    "aichat_settings": {
